title: Highway Frontage Retail Business and Residential Quarters
text:
Highway Frontage Retail Business and Residential Quarters ad date: 09/30/2015 
11950 Hwy 101, Crescent City, CA Fronting on 243 feet of highway frontage is a 3,460 sq.ft. retail/ commercial building & large attic area for storage, plus 1,050 sq. ft. basement with roll-up doors, retail area has coolers, shelving, ADA bathroom & more. Warehouse building is 2,100 sq. ft. on a slab with 2 roll-up doors & metal roof. Ideal as living quarters is a detached two story residence built in 1998 with 865 sq. ft., 1 bedroom, 1 bath on the second floor & 800 sq. ft. of wrap around decking & 800 sq. ft. garage. MLS 1365085 $550,000 Kurt Stremberg, Broker 785 E. Washington Blvd #2, Crescent City Office: 707-465-2121 Cell: 707-954-1732
